Job Description
Share
Be fully in charge in overseeing and directing all aspects of the kitchen operation in a 5 Star Luxury hotel in the quiet Heliopolis of Cairo, Egypt. Keep up with market trends. Ensure that all buffet and plating are executed with fresh, attractive designs that are consistently picture perfect.
The hotel features spa services, swimming pools, 300 guestrooms, and 9 FB outlets serving a wide range of cuisine including Egyptian, Lebanese, Italian, Indian, Sushi, and French inspired afternoon tea.
A versatile Executive Chef is needed with at least 5 years similar experience in the Middle East, Egypt preferred of course. The position is responsible for overseeing 100 cooks and 40 stewards as a patient trainer who communicates clearly in a manner that will motivate the team. Responsible for maintaining all food safety and hygiene standards while improving the SOPs and controlling food costs.
Desired Candidate Profile
The position offers an excellent expat package with salary in the US $55-65k range plus medical, dental, housing, etc. Europeans are highly encouraged to apply.
